  "notes": [
    "Schedule B (Form 1040) AcroForm widget map for the IRS-hosted TY2025 PDF (PDF /Title metadata: '2025 Schedule B (Form 1040)').",
    "TY2024-vs-TY2025 deltas: none observed. Schedule B has not changed line numbering since the 2020 restructure that introduced the foreign-account / foreign-trust questions in Part III.",
    "Part I line 1 and Part II line 5 are REPEATING-ROW tables: 14 payer rows in Part I and 15 payer rows in Part II. Each row has a payer-name widget (left/wide) and an amount widget (right/narrow). The map exposes these as `part_i_line_1_rows_widgets` and `part_ii_line_5_rows_widgets` arrays so Layer 2 can iterate.",
    "Schedule B Part III foreign-account / foreign-trust checkboxes are Yes/No PAIRS. Each Layer 1 boolean (`part_iii_line_7a_foreign_account`, `part_iii_line_7a_fincen114_required`, `part_iii_line_8_foreign_trust`) maps to the YES checkbox; the companion NO checkbox is in `unmapped_widgets`. Filling the form requires setting exactly ONE of each pair (callers' responsibility).",
    "Continuation: rows beyond Part I row 13 (or Part II row 14) cannot fit on the IRS PDF and require an attached statement \u2014 a follow-up."
  ],
